&lt;li&gt;Process distributor and dealer orders in SAP from order receipt through invoicing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitate customer orders and monitor the order fulfillment process to ensure timely and accurate delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Accurately enter, review, and process customer orders, ensuring all required information is complete.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor Salesforce for failed orders, correct errors, and release orders to SAP.&lt;/li&gt;
