&lt;li&gt;Complete inspection reports and maintain accurate documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct audits to ensure compliance with quality standards and procedures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with root cause investigations and corrective actions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support continuous improvement efforts throughout the manufacturing process.&lt;/li&gt;
