&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Company Summary:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Greenworks Tools is the leader in battery-powered outdoor power tools for DIY-consumers and landscaping professionals. The company distributes Greenworks branded and private label products, as well as products for an extensive network of Original Equipment Manufacturers. With a robust line of Greenworks branded products, including 24-volt, 40-volt, 60-volt, 80-volt, and commercial grade 82-volt battery-powered outdoor power equipment, a full line of corded equipment, and power tools. Utilizing best-in-class technology, Greenworks tools deliver the power and performance of comparable gas-powered tools without issues associated with gas products. For more information, find us on the web at greenworkstools.com or greenworkscommercial.com.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
